BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Even Petra became one of the kindest kids in Willowbrook.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (After Lina's kindness had reached her, Petra started being gentle with others too.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (She apologized to the kids she'd teased. She shared her new clothes with a girl whose) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (family couldn't afford many.) Tj ET
