BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 20) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (By the end of that year, the Garden of Kindness was the most beautiful place anyone had) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (ever seen.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (It had overflowed its stone walls and flowers were growing all through the park, along the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (streets, in window boxes all over town.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (The whole town of Willowbrook was a garden now, because the whole town had become kind.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (And it all started with one girl, one smile, and one compliment about bread.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.4 Td ([Illustration: An aerial view of Willowbrook completely covered in flowers   growing from) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td (buildings, along streets, in every window   the whole town transformed into a garden of) Tj ET
