stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 21) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Grandmother found Lina sitting in the garden one evening, surrounded by a thousand) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (flowers.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td ('You did this, my sweet girl,' Grandmother said, sitting beside her.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td ('No,' Lina shook her head with a smile. 'I only planted the first seed. Everyone else grew) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (the garden.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td ('And that,' said Grandmother, 'is the most beautiful thing about kindness. One small seed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (can grow into a whole world of flowers.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td ('All you have to do is plant it.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: Grandmother and Lina sitting together on a bench in the magnificent garden) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (at sunset, surrounded by thousands of colorful flowers, a peaceful and beautiful closing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (scene]) Tj ET
