stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 22) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Now here's a secret just for you, dear reader:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (There's a Garden of Kindness in YOUR town too. You can't see it with your eyes, but it's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (there.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (Every time you're kind   every smile, every helping hand, every gentle word   a flower) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (blooms somewhere invisible.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (And when you're kind, you inspire others to be kind too. That's how the garden grows.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (So go ahead. Plant your first seed today. Say something nice. Help someone. Share what you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (have. And watch your world bloom.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: A child reader looking out at their own neighborhood, imagining invisible) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (flowers blooming everywhere people are being kind, a magical overlay of the reader's own) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (world becoming a garden]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
