stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 23) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Here are some seeds you can plant right now, today:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Smile at someone who looks lonely. Hold the door for a stranger. Say thank you and really) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (mean it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (Draw a picture for someone who is sad. Share your snack with a friend. Listen when someone) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (needs to talk.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (Tell someone what you love about them. Help without being asked. Forgive someone who hurt) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (you.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (Every single one of these is a flower waiting to bloom. And YOU are the gardener.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: A child planting invisible seeds of kindness that grow into beautiful) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (flowers around them   each kind act depicted as a colorful bloom, the child surrounded by) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (a garden of their own making]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
