stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 24) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And remember what Lina learned: the hardest kindness grows the biggest flowers.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Being kind to someone who is mean to you. Forgiving someone who hurt you. Helping someone) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (who never helped you back.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (Those are the sunflower seeds   the ones that grow tall and golden and spectacular.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (You do not have to be perfect. You do not have to be kind every single second. But every) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (time you choose kindness over cruelty, love over anger, gentleness over harshness...) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (Your garden grows. And so does the world.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: A final beautiful image of a garden in full bloom with the sun shining) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (through, a quote carved in stone: 'Kindness grows when you share it,' Lina and her) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (grandmother visible in the distance]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
