BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 25) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (One more thing from Lina to you:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (You will have days when being kind feels hard. Days when someone is mean and you want to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (be mean back.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (On those days, remember the sunflower   the biggest, most beautiful flower in the whole) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (garden. The one that grew when Lina chose kindness even when it was difficult.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (Difficult kindness grows the most spectacular flowers. So on hard days, choose kindness) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (anyway.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (Your garden is counting on you. And it will be magnificent.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: A single spectacular sunflower standing tall in a garden, representing the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (beauty that grows from choosing kindness on difficult days, golden and radiant, inspiring) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (and warm]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
