stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Kindness Grows When You Share It) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (Lina showed us that one small act of kindness can start something incredible. When you're) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (kind to someone, they feel good and want to be kind to someone else. And that person) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (passes it along too! Before you know it, one tiny seed of kindness has grown into a whole) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (garden that makes everyone's life more beautiful. You don't have to do big, grand things.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (Just smile. Just help. Just be gentle. The garden will do the rest.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
