stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Discussion Questions for Parents) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (After reading this story together, talk about these questions:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.4 Td (1. What kind thing could you do tomorrow to 'plant a seed' in your own garden of kindness?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.6 Td (2. Has someone ever been kind to you when you were having a bad day? How did it make you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.6 Td (feel?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.8 Td (3. Why do you think Lina's kindness to Petra \(who was mean to her\) grew the biggest) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.8 Td (flower?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 557.0 Td (4. Can you think of a time when one person's kindness made lots of other people happier) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 543.0 Td (too?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 519.2 Td (5. If you had a Garden of Kindness, what colors do you think your flowers would be?) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
